sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Customer
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as Laravel API
  participant DB as RDS
  participant Pay as PaySvc (Gateway)
  participant PSP as PSP (MoMo)
  participant Project as ProjectSvc
  participant Split as PaymentSplitSvc
  participant Wallet as WalletSvc

  U->>FE: Accept recommended hardware + request installer -> submit order
  FE->>API: POST /projects {estimation_id, hardware_list, installer_id}
  API->>DB: create project, create payment_plan (milestone type), create milestones
  API-->>FE: project created + payment_plan + milestones

  U->>FE: Pays installment for Milestone #1 (amount X)
  FE->>API: POST /payments {milestone_id, amount, method=momo}
  API->>Pay: create payment record & call PSP (redirect / initiate)
  Pay->>PSP: initiate transaction
  PSP-->>Pay: webhook -> success
  Pay->>DB: update payment (status=success)
  Pay->>Split: create PaymentSplit entries (provider/installer/platform)
  Split->>Wallet: credit internal wallets (or call PSP transfer APIs)
  Wallet->>DB: update balances, create Transaction ledger records
  Split-->>API: settled for that installment
  API->>DB: update milestone.total_paid (sum installments)
  alt milestone.total_paid >= milestone.amount
    API->>DB: set milestone.status = completed
    API->>Project: if all milestones completed set project.status = completed
  end
  API-->>FE: payment success + milestone progress
